  5. Rogers Hornsby, 175 <br>
  6. Mickey Mantle, 172 <br>
  7. Dan Brouthers, 170 <br>
  8. Joe Jackson, 169 <br>
  9. Ty Cobb, 168 <br>
 10. Pete Browning, Jimmie Foxx & Mark McGwire, 163
